{
  "stem": "617.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the ones they select, they would tell them to go, come out of the line, and go to another place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my sister and I were never selected, because we were so run-down by then.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were not good for work anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the ones which were not selected, in Stutthof, there was like an infirmary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Stutthof also had a lot of gypsies inmates.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the gypsies were sort of even taking care of us, you know, like we were below.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So people who were not selected for work, they would take them over to the infirmary, which the infirmary was a big wire fence, a high wire fence with a big gate of wire, like a wire fence gate.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a gypsy would stand at the gates so no one could go in, no one could go out, without their allowing that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember, my sister and I were sent there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And by that time, we knew, you're never allowed to say you're sick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You're never allowed to say you're weak.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You're always strong, and you could always manage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we saw ourselves in the infirmary there, with sick people who were in their bunks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And every morning-- like, we stayed there an overnight-- the next morning, they would take all the dead and the sick, and they would take them on carts and take them out to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Of course--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Stutthof, there was one crematorium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because there was only one crematorium, they couldn't burn so many at once.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So first, they would take the dead, and then the sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, you know, they had a quota.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So many.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They would take the others who were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Therefore, it was a dangerous place to be.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
